  "title": "chore(stories): add categories",
  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis adds sections in our Storybook following the same organization as the [documentation API ref](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/js/).\r\n\r\nNote that this **updates the stories URLs** and therefore we need to update the documentation links for v4.\r\n\r\nLet me know if you want to go that route so that I PR the doc repo.\r\n\r\n## Preview\r\n\r\n[See stories →](https://deploy-preview-4154--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories)",
